summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and Comptroller of the City of Seattle, on behalf of the City of Seattle, to execute a quit claim deed to C. Debrits, for Lot Three (3), Block Two (2) Monroe's First Addition to the City of Seattle, less the west ten (10) feet, in consideration of the repayment to the City of Seattle by said C. Debritz of certain money paid by said City to the Treasurer of King County for general taxes.
